Investment Traction

Broad Interest from Diverse Investment Groups in Our Project:

CPC and RTO Offers: We have received several Capital Pool Company (CPC) offers and two Reverse Takeover (RTO) offers, with valuations ranging from CAD 24M to CAD 55M.
GEM Digital Limited Offering: A $20M investment proposal from GEM Digital Limited, a digital asset investment firm in The Bahamas, part of the $3.4 billion Global Emerging Markets group.
Pharmacy Investment: The CEO of Uniprix (a group of 560 pharmacies) is a shareholder and has secured $1M from four pharmacists, with more expressing interest in investing.
Web3 VC Discussions: Engaged in numerous discussions with Web3 venture capital firms eager to explore investment opportunities in our project.
